Doctor wants me to get my busted back examined and it’s gonna cost me. I’m looking to do 4 pfp commissions at around 25$ a pop to cover the exam. 

Here’s some older work for reference http://artstation.com/starxvii

Please feel free to message me here or on twitter as I am more active there.

You can find me on twitter @Star_XVII

Thanks everyone, 
take it easy will ya?
